short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: ScubaDuba is a captivating browser extension that immerses you in the underwater world of scuba diving.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The best extension to brighten up your day with wonderful backgrounds of nature landscapes, the Ocean, and some Diving!

The ScubaDuba extension sets different ocean and scuba-themed backgrounds for your new page. 
Users can shuffle the backgrounds by clicking the button on the top right corner of the screen. 

By clicking "Add to Chrome" I accept and agree to install the ScubaDuba Chrome extension and hereby agree to set the Chrome New Tab to that provided by the service and the Privacy policy and Terms of Use.
The search results will be provided by Yahoo.
